  <?dbhtml filename="gst10-plugins-base.html"?>

  <title>gst-plugins-base-&gst10-plugins-base-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The GStreamer Base Plug-ins is a well-groomed and well-maintained
      collection of GStreamer plug-ins and elements, spanning the range of
      possible types of elements one would want to write for GStreamer. You
      will need at least one of Good, Bad, Ugly or Libav plugins for GStreamer
      applications to function properly.
    </para>

